{"tid":1245880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］聽我講一句 關於聽日去野餐","createTime":"2019-06-20T13:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T18:48:45.000Z","uid":158260,"like":774,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"17b1d2272eb0091b2fc09e1085dba08cee8fec77","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"回應返【2032】政府晚上宣布，基於保安考慮，政總明日暫停開放。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地聽日可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暫緩衝擊行動</span></strong></span>正所謂敵不動我不動。既然政府叫左D人聽日唔洗返，都好難再彈出彈入叫人再返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地不如就將計就計，聽日唔撚衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改做後日先再去夢遊野餐，到時就睇班狗仔係到企下企下係到曬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地就休養生息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae512cf2c889722464c95caee21135be09937f8","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd479f57b5648f5f90350c040f404d3be7f762cb","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38fbab62aeaaac318c85d7eefb0a6e45249924c8","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"推到有人見到"},{"pid":"baf51651910a6010fdd00a77a0d52bc31143a5d9","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdb18bcfbc4d099136ac1b4f94814bd9961d9543","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46b0ba43221aa90d31a0975aed2849d3ae9492a7","tid":1245880,"uid":158260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-